        Create, update, or truncate an analysis with provided questions or and/or question names
        Parameters:
        containerName - The container in which the analysis resides
        newAnalysis - Whether or not to create a new analysis. Incompatible with delQuestionsStr.
        aName - The name of the analysis
        questionsToAdd - The questions to be added to or initially populate the analysis.
        questionsToDelete - A list of question names to be deleted from the analysis. Incompatible with newAnalysis.
        suggested - An optional Boolean indicating whether analysis is suggested (default: false).
